title: The Three Stooges - No Census, No Feeling

sources.description: The Three Stooges - No Census, No Feeling (1940) IN COLOR! The boys are accidentally assigned as census takers in their town. Chaos ensues as their bumbling methods lead to confusion and mishaps while attempting to count every household. From mistaken identities to slapstick encounters, the boysâ€™ antics turn the ordinary task of census taking into a hilarious disaster. Colorized and digitally enhanced as God intended.
